channel.title: Uploading my RSPS!
channel.description:
Hey,
So I'm almost finished coding my RSPS however I've noticed that on other RSPS clients you only see the .class files, is there a way to archive my client while excluding all the .java files at the same time? Please and Thanks!
P.S. I'm using Winrar to Archive and I'm uploading to Mediafire.

item.title: Uploading my RSPS!
item.dc:creator: @runescape_sucks runescape sucks
item.description:
@runescape_sucks wrote:

You could delete all the .java files…
Just make a copy that you can edit, and when you finish editing paste the .class files into the copied one
